  <!-- ═══ FRE Welcome Page ═══ -->
  <data name="FreOverlay_WelcomeTitle.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Nāu mai ki Intelligent Terminal</value>
    <comment>{Locked=qps-ploc,qps-ploca,qps-plocm} "Intelligent Terminal" is the product name.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_WelcomeSubtitlePrefix" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Whakaritea tō kaitiaki mō-roto hei āwhina i a koe ki te whakamarama i ngā hapa, tuhi tono, me te wewete mahi i te wāhi e mahi ana koe. </value>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_WelcomeSubtitleLink" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>He atu kōrero mō Intelligent Terminal</value>
    <comment>{Locked=qps-ploc,qps-ploca,qps-plocm} "Intelligent Terminal" is the product name.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card1Title.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Noho i te rere me tō kaitiaki AI mō-roto</value>
    <comment>In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card1Description.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Ka tirotiro tō kaitiaki i ngā mea e pā ana i tō tauranga, ā ka taea te āwhina i a koe ki te mārama me te whakatika i ngā hapa ka puta.</value>
    <comment>In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card2Title.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Haere tonu mai i te wāhi i mutu ai koe</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card2Description.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Tirohia ngā wāhanga kaitiaki kei te mahi me ngā mea o mua ka hoki ki tō mahi i roto i ngā hekenatia. Tirohia ngā mahi kei te haere, arā tirohia anō ngā mahi o mua me te kore e ngaro i tō tūranga.</value>
    <comment>In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_NextButton.Content" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Panuku</value>
  </data>
